{"TopicId":95264,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Found a good temporary IVA for the Mk3 cockpit","CreatedByName":"montyben101","CreatedById":74173,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-01T14:29:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"montyben101","CreatedById":74173,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-01T14:29:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you download the CSS mod (link in my sig) You can put the IVA in the squad spaces folder, put the props in the props folder and then change the line in the config from this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EINTERNAL\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E{\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E name = Placeholder\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E}\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eto this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EINTERNAL\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E{\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E name = css_cockpit\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E}\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt works really well, you should also have RPM installed to get the displays to work\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-01T14:34:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECan we see a screenshot?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"montyben101","CreatedById":74173,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-01T16:02:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i59.tinypic.com/4jo80.png\u0022 alt=\u00224jo80.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i57.tinypic.com/mu7tlc.png\u0022 alt=\u0022mu7tlc.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}